raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "8.4.1" %}

package:
  name: ipyparallel
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/i/ipyparallel/ipyparallel-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 670bbe05755381742e1ea01177dc428ff8f3e94af1f0d5642c9d19f37ca8289b

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script_env:
    - IPP_DISABLE_JS=1
  entry_points:
    - ipcluster = ipyparallel.cluster.app:main
    - ipcontroller = ipyparallel.controller.app:main
    - ipengine = ipyparallel.engine.app:main
  script:
    - {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install -vv --no-deps .

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.6
    - pip
    - hatchling >=0.25
    - jupyterlab ==3.*
  run:
    - python >=3.6
    - decorator
    - tornado >=5.1
    - python-dateutil >=2.1
    - pyzmq >=18
    - ipython >=6
    - jupyter_client
    - ipykernel >=4.4
    - traitlets >=4.3
    - psutil
    - tqdm
    - entrypoints

test:
  requires:
    - jupyterlab ==3.*
    - notebook >=5.3
    - pip
    - m2-grep  # [win]
  imports:
    - ipyparallel
    - ipyparallel.apps
    - ipyparallel.client
    - ipyparallel.controller
    - ipyparallel.engine
    - ipyparallel.serialize
  commands:
    - ipcluster -h
    - ipengine -h
    - ipcontroller -h
    - pip check
    # list
    - jupyter labextension list
    - jupyter server extension list
    - jupyter serverextension list
    # validate
    - jupyter labextension list 1>labextensions 2>&1
    - jupyter server extension list 1>server_extensions 2>&1
    - jupyter serverextension list 1>serverextensions 2>&1
    - grep -ie "ipyparallel-labextension.*v{{ version.replace(".", "\\.") }}.*OK" labextensions
    - grep -ie "ipyparallel.*{{ version.replace(".", "\\.") }}.*OK" server_extensions
    - grep -ie "ipyparallel.*{{ version.replace(".", "\\.") }}.*OK" serverextensions

about:
  home: https://github.com/ipython/ipyparallel
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file:
    - COPYING.md
    - ipyparallel/labextension/static/third-party-licenses.json
  license_family: BSD
  summary: Interactive Parallel Computing with IPython
  doc_url: https://ipyparallel.readthedocs.io
  dev_url: https://github.com/ipython/ipyparallel

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
    - minrk
    - bollwyvl
